  "body": "Could be useful for additional data availability -- in case relay which sent the bid can't retrieve the payload, other relays might still possess them, even if they haven't sent the bid.\r\n\r\nOnly downside I can see is that it will cause light additional load and logging on all relays, if getPayload gets called on all of them for most slots. Doesn't seem big of a downside really.",
